data.description: You will not want to miss this charming , fully updated Victorian style 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home in peaceful Marion, Texas! The backyard is an entertainer's dream with a sparkling in-ground pool and sports court to live out your hoop dreams. The detached garage is great for larger vehicles, storage, and/or a shop. Inside you will love the farmhouse appeal!  All of the bedrooms are larger than the average sized bedroom so they're perfect to be used as bedrooms or an office if needed.  Each of the 3 bathrooms have been fully remodeled.  The master bedroom is downstairs and convenient for any buyer! Take advantage of the open kitchen and living space to enjoy time with friends , family , or just good ole peaceful alone time. Come scoop this one up while you can!
